== Configuration ==

Vim can be configured on per-user basis or via global defaults.

=== Global ===

The global configuration file for Vim can be found at {{Path|/etc/vim/vimrc}}

=== User ===

The each user's configuration file should be located at {{Path|~/.vimrc}} (the base of the user's home directory).

